EXPLANATION
BY THE LEGISLATIVE COUNCIL
OF
A N A C T
RELATING TO BUSINESSES AND PROFESSIONS -- THE HUMAN TRAFFICKING
PREVENTION NOTICE ACT
***
1 This act would require hotel employees and short-term rental property operators to
2 annually receive human trafficking awareness training. The operator of the premises shall maintain
3 records of the completed training.
4 This act would take effect on January 1, 2026.
